the sky flickers orange and black over the bridge 
at muxidi as flames roll through two buses bullets whistle and 
zing tear gas canisters boom fascists fascists chants the 
crowd 
the peoples liberation army has entered beijing to liberate the 
city from the people 
bloodied residents sprawled on threewheeled pedicabs are 
