judge at between 108018 and 130300 
myron bright a semiretired appeals judge in fargo nd 
receives a 95000 judicial salary and made more than 43530 from 
teaching and speaking in 1987 his total income was more than the 
combined salaries of north dakotas chief justice and attorney 
general 
personal finance isnt the lure for many of the attorneys who 
accept a lifetime appointment as judge on an actual income 
basis i think im making less than i did when i first got on the 
bench said the 70yearold bright but im not complaining 
